 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seeger.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seeger.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seeger.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seeger.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 5817, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/12/14/roll-of-the-dice-incident-on-57th-street/", "url_meta": {"origin": 11630, "position": 3}, "title": "Roll of the Dice: Incident on 57th Street", "author": "Ken", "date": "December 14, 2018", "format": false, "excerpt": "Most artists spend their career working toward a pinnacle like \u201cIncident in 57th Street.\u201d Bruce recorded his on his 24th birthday.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Roll of the Dice&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Roll of the Dice", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/roll-of-the-dice/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/incident.jpg?fit=913%2C719&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/incident.jpg?fit=913%2C719&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/incident.jpg?fit=913%2C719&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/incident.jpg?fit=913%2C719&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 7433, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/02/15/cover-me-rumble/", "url_meta": {"origin": 11630, "position": 4}, "title": "Cover Me: Rumble", "author": "Ken", "date": "February 15, 2019", "format": false, "excerpt": "Shortly after Link Wray's death in 2005, Bruce paid homage by opening